GET {{tours}}?travelStyle[all]=Adventure&travelStyle[all]=Mountain Hikes  HTTP/1.1


### filter query 2
GET {{tours}}?price[lt]=1000&rating[gte]=2   HTTP/1.1


### sort query					
GET {{tours}}?sort=-price HTTP/1.1

### select fields
GET {{tours}}
?fields=name,duration,summary,price
